LOved it!!!! Their food is delicious!!! I went with a friend who used to live in Greece and he reccomended some specific dishes and i was in love with them!! I cant recall the names but we had the spinach pita, olives some dip that was extremely good and a great dessert!! The place is gorgeous, it just makes you want to relax and have fun and be happy!! we had wine as well that was very good, service excellent!! All in one it was one of my best experiences in a restaurant!! Going back soon!!
